# Local dev only. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in ONE token option.
# In production these are set on the Cloudflare Pages project (Settings →
# Variables and Secrets), not from this file.
# Used by: npx wrangler pages dev public
#
# If you were issued a long-life access token:
RTT_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-long-life-access-token
#
# If you were issued a refresh token instead (leave RTT_ACCESS_TOKEN blank):
# RTT_REFRESH_TOKEN=your-refresh-token
#
# Optional: pin the API version (ISO date). Leave unset to always use the latest.
# RTT_API_VERSION=2026-04-09
